  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a whimsical world of hopping fun and ribbiting excitement in Froggies at the Zoo! Join our charming amphibian friends on a delightful adventure that will have you leaping with joy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📸 Hop and Snap with Froggy Cam: Get ready to capture every moment of your frog-tastic journey with the revolutionary Froggy Cam! Immerse yourself in the action like never before by taking control of an in-game camera. Zoom, pan and snap adorable snapshots of your froggies as they bound through lush environments and conquer puzzling challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐸 Leap into Adventure: Embark on an unforgettable journey with 9 unique levels as you snap a group of adorable froggies through a series of photo challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/6e9500818c86acfd9d2350adaebb08e7.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/6e9500818c86acfd9d2350adaebb08e7.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/6e9500818c86acfd9d2350adaebb08e7.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 Frog-tastic Environments: Explore vibrant and lush environments, each brimming with interactive elements and hidden secrets. Discover exotic flora, encounter different frogs, and uncover hidden pathways as you leap your way through this enchanting world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/2edc2a79dbe0d75c065e93c75bb58112.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/2edc2a79dbe0d75c065e93c75bb58112.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/2edc2a79dbe0d75c065e93c75bb58112.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎵 Ribbiting Soundtrack: Immerse yourself in the enchanting sounds of the froggy world, featuring a lively and catchy soundtrack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/b2f24ba2f005f36595111bd45e389819.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/b2f24ba2f005f36595111bd45e389819.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/b2f24ba2f005f36595111bd45e389819.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐸 Unleash your inner frog and get ready for a leap of a lifetime in Froggies at the Zoo! Are you ready to hop to it and take some photos? 🐸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a whimsical world of hopping fun and ribbiting excitement in Froggies at the Zoo! Join our charming amphibian friends on a delightful adventure that will have you leaping with joy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📸 Hop and Snap with Froggy Cam: Get ready to capture every moment of your frog-tastic journey with the revolutionary Froggy Cam! Immerse yourself in the action like never before by taking control of an in-game camera. Zoom, pan and snap adorable snapshots of your froggies as they bound through lush environments and conquer puzzling challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/1943279955594ac82ddb79dcef3fe73d.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐸 Leap into Adventure: Embark on an unforgettable journey with 9 unique levels as you snap a group of adorable froggies through a series of photo challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/6e9500818c86acfd9d2350adaebb08e7.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/6e9500818c86acfd9d2350adaebb08e7.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic