o! Are you ready to hop to it and take some photos? 🐸</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.poster.avif?t=1738701062\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.webm?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2566620/extras/8f4c60baa546bffe6ed5776c76120b5f.mp4?t=1738701062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
